Cell["\<\
So, there are two choices and an arbitrary sign for the transformation \
(noticing that these amount
to moving into sum/difference coordinates, these amount to choosing which \
order you want the difference to be and which direction is positive)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.969118058042831*^9, 
  3.969118121941807*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"49b0ebdd-717b-4325-8f45-\
5fa6aa50460c"],

